{"id": "ChIJ86AUkzyQj4ARcQ-ARqJ5Dcc", "rating": 4.3, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 299, "displayName": {"text": "Chinese Bakery & Deli", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Old-school bakeshop serving traditional Chinese desserts, treats & fare in an unpretentious setting.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ86AUkzyQj4ARcQ-ARqJ5Dcc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paSVVFVjBNVW94WDNaaU5VNHhSMHRFU0hsVmNIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I got there in the afternoon around 2:10pm on a Tuesday and there was a line of about 10 people in front of me.\n\nI ordered a dozen chicken sandwiches, fish sandwiches, egg tarts, hotdog bun, pineapple bun with red bean paste filling. The prices are reasonable.\n\nThe chicken sandwich gets a 7.5/10. The chicken is moist, white sauce they used on it is good not too overpowering but most of the sauce ends up at the backside of the bun. If they added an option to add a pickle then it would be an 8.5/10.\n\nThe fish sandwich gets a 8/10. Fish sandwich is crispy on the outside especially near the outer edges, moist on the inside. Same white sauce used on both sandwiches.\n\nEgg custard were delicious, not too sweet and the crust is flaky but the price is a bit on the expensive side (believe it was $2 for just one). Taste is 8/10, price is 4/10\n\nHotdog bun is the same as everywhere. Nothing special. 6/10\n\nPineapple bun is a bit dry. The red bean paste is just a round paste on the inside, not evenly distributed. 5.5/10\n\nParking lot has a ton of parking.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I got there in the afternoon around 2:10pm on a Tuesday and there was a line of about 10 people in front of me.\n\nI ordered a dozen chicken sandwiches, fish sandwiches, egg tarts, hotdog bun, pineapple bun with red bean paste filling. The prices are reasonable.\n\nThe chicken sandwich gets a 7.5/10. The chicken is moist, white sauce they used on it is good not too overpowering but most of the sauce ends up at the backside of the bun. If they added an option to add a pickle then it would be an 8.5/10.\n\nThe fish sandwich gets a 8/10. Fish sandwich is crispy on the outside especially near the outer edges, moist on the inside. Same white sauce used on both sandwiches.\n\nEgg custard were delicious, not too sweet and the crust is flaky but the price is a bit on the expensive side (believe it was $2 for just one). Taste is 8/10, price is 4/10\n\nHotdog bun is the same as everywhere. Nothing special. 6/10\n\nPineapple bun is a bit dry. The red bean paste is just a round paste on the inside, not evenly distributed. 5.5/10\n\nParking lot has a ton of parking.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tommy", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108440974079431826544/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3e3SaAoKaY6TrdFkqd3RSRChpTFXw6v_AXrvKXMb_6ZAah1k=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-20T08:27:34.525434909Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paSVVFVjBNVW94WDNaaU5VNHhSMHRFU0hsVmNIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paSVVFVjBNVW94WDNaaU5VNHhSMHRFU0hsVmNIYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f903c9314a0f3:0xc70d79a246800f71"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ86AUkzyQj4ARcQ-ARqJ5Dcc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WeGQyUm5UMFZuWWtORVZVbFpaVFp5VlRkU1RGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place is really awesome! No frills, cheap, and delicious fresh, soft bread. They specialize in fried fish sandwiches. It cost $3.50. I liked it much better than the chicken breast one which is not as moist and tender as the fish. It’s super trendy right now so you have to go during non-peak hours otherwise there are crazy long lines. I went on a weekday right before the lunch rush and I only had to wait about 10 minutes. Their butter pineapple buns and green onions buns are also really good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place is really awesome! No frills, cheap, and delicious fresh, soft bread. They specialize in fried fish sandwiches. It cost $3.50. I liked it much better than the chicken breast one which is not as moist and tender as the fish. It’s super trendy right now so you have to go during non-peak hours otherwise there are crazy long lines. I went on a weekday right before the lunch rush and I only had to wait about 10 minutes. Their butter pineapple buns and green onions buns are also really good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Shane T. Barclay", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114435412104418525229/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlTLnFyl-VxhTF8cZ_8vN-rJnZfimTfeydoMFYaYLON0Vu1A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-04T16:49:11.354932916Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WeGQyUm5UMFZuWWtORVZVbFpaVFp5VlRkU1RGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WeGQyUm5UMFZuWWtORVZVbFpaVFp5VlRkU1RGRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f903c9314a0f3:0xc70d79a246800f71"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ86AUkzyQj4ARcQ-ARqJ5Dcc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oR1gwWnZjMHhLYVhOdlduWkhjR2R4VkV3d1JVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place is about business.  I love it. Arrived early to beat the line, and see what the hoop-la was all about. They were open early, which was awesome.  We'll, im definitely a fan!  The fish sandwich was so definitely worth the money. I quickly ate 2 and realized they were fresh, and on a warm bun that was just prepared a few minutes before.  I do suggest that you come with some patience because the traffic is non-stop and people are flowing in and out. They have 3 registers to speed up the line. This is not a place to sit down and eat, so be prepared to grab and go. Customer service is friendly and seemed to welcome a quick hello, as they prepared my order.  Some items sell out quickly,  so pretty order, or call ahead so your not disappointed.  Enjoy!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place is about business.  I love it. Arrived early to beat the line, and see what the hoop-la was all about. They were open early, which was awesome.  We'll, im definitely a fan!  The fish sandwich was so definitely worth the money. I quickly ate 2 and realized they were fresh, and on a warm bun that was just prepared a few minutes before.  I do suggest that you come with some patience because the traffic is non-stop and people are flowing in and out. They have 3 registers to speed up the line. This is not a place to sit down and eat, so be prepared to grab and go. Customer service is friendly and seemed to welcome a quick hello, as they prepared my order.  Some items sell out quickly,  so pretty order, or call ahead so your not disappointed.  Enjoy!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Stan Mayfield", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104170454366309359127/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUOhCp4u8pE7hJb2gBmntloNzrxSB6_mx2ZM2aQI03JeXT0HK5=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-05T14:56:06.419504489Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oR1gwWnZjMHhLYVhOdlduWkhjR2R4VkV3d1JVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oR1gwWnZjMHhLYVhOdlduWkhjR2R4VkV3d1JVRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f903c9314a0f3:0xc70d79a246800f71"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ86AUkzyQj4ARcQ-ARqJ5Dcc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SdU1XZGlUMkV6VEU5TVpqZFBZMGh5UjBScVltYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Came here to say that the drive is worth it. It was breakfast for me . Each sandwich [whether chicken or fish] is 3.50 each ! So good.. they’re quick work service and the wait was not bad. Came here on a Saturday morning at 10-11am. Both sandwiches come with a mayo nothing special but cheap, and just the right amount of everything! Even eating it hours later it was was still crispy and it is not overly friend. Perfection!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came here to say that the drive is worth it. It was breakfast for me . Each sandwich [whether chicken or fish] is 3.50 each ! So good.. they’re quick work service and the wait was not bad. Came here on a Saturday morning at 10-11am. Both sandwiches come with a mayo nothing special but cheap, and just the right amount of everything! Even eating it hours later it was was still crispy and it is not overly friend. Perfection!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chellies Tran", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107976763696036071361/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlUgg9CXvs-cAJr1MSP1uuayvtzH59z9aIBJKcRcbk6uSM_Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-24T03:47:28.616707018Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SdU1XZGlUMkV6VEU5TVpqZFBZMGh5UjBScVltYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SdU1XZGlUMkV6VEU5TVpqZFBZMGh5UjBScVltYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f903c9314a0f3:0xc70d79a246800f71"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ86AUkzyQj4ARcQ-ARqJ5Dcc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSTFdHNVlRV1UwUWkxVVVVODRaRms0UVRSU1ExRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Very tasty fried “fish-wich” style sandwich. Probably the best thing on the menu. Decent egg custard tarts, hot dog buns, and sesame balls. Most other items were pretty typical of most Chinese bakeries. Great pricing.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very tasty fried “fish-wich” style sandwich. Probably the best thing on the menu. Decent egg custard tarts, hot dog buns, and sesame balls. Most other items were pretty typical of most Chinese bakeries. Great pricing.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jo Fis", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109866247632127731663/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLk1MAlquF6f2WcnJi9VDibF8NzpsnBFLSQjUnZFSzjnVpq4Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-07T01:32:19.191171894Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSTFdHNVlRV1UwUWkxVVVVODRaRms0UVRSU1ExRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSTFdHNVlRV1UwUWkxVVVVODRaRms0UVRSU1ExRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f903c9314a0f3:0xc70d79a246800f71"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ86AUkzyQj4ARcQ-ARqJ5Dcc/photos/AWCwydgUe21Ab-DFt2mmRJkYQLLAJ3VkpluRdsX5IWmcyCwvBrJ4N3v-24Ktl9XY0i4wcr6i3TAKO_sYD1ez7e-tl6MTj8rWC6pqb-_lCenZYGyMIuSVVfwh_d_1YWFDH6yeExH49X0exFaWaRX5vDnvVwvarIHKYW8YnrRgPvaDx4soxtnlaG22AZtMrTXR9LjIBGKtIl-wdBVEAWnm8EH7FotIBGoLaXaexHrQH4DfsxJ59tMIqIAqRzUt9E6_dCAzeqU3L3jiX4001tWFx7FhhPtKfvW27csjuy36ILcoNW8vryegAJW-Wya2BoVsFqJYgA2OibKySXi3rExpZG2q8eA2CufAlmvntCEx4GW6YL-Kak2T3BuT8omwbIZDjt9g4LfCioDjJ3O9EIU9BdRgg3u9cQGklKti9IAWJpjFc-448MP6", "widthPx": 3024, "heightPx": 4032, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Chinese Bakery & Deli", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/107481306432633399023", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkLFA6Nb5tvGEgUgoep_HBDj89uA3uaval1ors23LuQc9NtQ=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgIDeuJi8uQE&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places